para: Sherlock Holmes is hired by the King of Bohemia to retrieve a compromising photograph from a certain lady The King has tried to purchase the photo and even hired burglars to retrieve it, but without success The woman in question is the very beautiful Irene Adler, an opera singer She has made no demands of the King so it does not seem that blackmail is her intent Using varioSherlock Holmes is hired by the King of Bohemia to retrieve a compromising photograph from a certain lady The King has tried to purchase the photo and even hired burglars to retrieve it, but without success The woman in question is the very beautiful Irene Adler, an opera singer She has made no demands of the King so it does not seem that blackmail is her intent Using vario
